Author: jasr0se
Text: I feel your pain. I used to work at Whole Foods. At the end of every shift I'd buy binge food to take home. It sucked because not only was I bingeing all the time, but I was also spending most of my paycheck on their expensive ass food haha.

Author: sweatyandsweet
Text: I like working around food, for some reason it just turns me off eating. I think it's just over-exposure to food. The same reason I'll watch mubangs if I feel hungry but don't want to eat.
